data.description: Discover an extraordinary investment opportunity nestled in the heart of New Bedford, MA.   All 3 units consist of 4 bedrooms, living room, kitchen, and bathroom. Updated Gas heating, hardwood floors, off street parking.  Easy access to shopping areas, including Market Basket; close to the highway, and a block away from the park. First Open house Saturday April 6 from 12:00-1:30pm and Sunday April 7 from 12:00 - 1:30pm.
